- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the PSA algorithm can be seen as a type of machine learning algorithm. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the PSA algorithm can be seen as a type of AI algorithm. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with optimization problems that can be seen as control problems.
